      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-4">
        <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm">
          &copy; 2011-{currentYear} CenturySync, Apiruck LLC. All rights reserved.
        </p>
        <div class="flex space-x-6 text-sm">
          <a href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}/privacy-policy`} class="text-gray-500 hover:text-white transition-colors duration-150 ease-stripe">Privacy Policy</a>
          <a href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}/terms-of-service`} class="text-gray-500 hover:text-white transition-colors duration-150 ease-stripe">Terms of Service</a>
